Dialogue: 1,0:00:00.48,0:00:07.99,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}どこまでいけるか分からないけど
Dialogue: 1,0:00:15.16,0:00:21.04,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}大丈夫　一人だっていいけど
Dialogue: 1,0:00:21.75,0:00:28.22,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}本当はね　誰も一人じゃない
Dialogue: 1,0:00:28.22,0:00:34.39,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}幸せが　寂しさが　不安も
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.81,0:00:43.94,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}全部味わうために生まれた
Dialogue: 1,0:00:44.57,0:00:47.78,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}一匙のきらめきで
Dialogue: 1,0:00:47.78,0:00:50.91,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}微笑みに変えていく
Dialogue: 1,0:00:50.91,0:00:57.70,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}それは密かに願い込めた
Dialogue: 1,0:00:58.00,0:01:00.71,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}奇跡かも
Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.96,0:01:07.67,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}一番大事な宝物を
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.67,0:01:13.97,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}見つけていくことが僕らの旅
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.97,0:01:20.69,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}どこまでいけるか分からないけど
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.19,0:01:29.24,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}目の前の今を希望で紡ぐよ
Dialogue: 1,0:00:00.48,0:00:07.99,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}雖不知能走多遠
Dialogue: 1,0:00:15.16,0:00:21.04,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}沒關係  一個人也能過得很好
Dialogue: 1,0:00:21.75,0:00:28.22,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}但其實  沒有人是孤獨的
Dialogue: 1,0:00:28.22,0:00:34.39,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}幸福  寂寞  擔憂
Dialogue: 1,0:00:34.81,0:00:43.94,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}都是人生的必由之路
Dialogue: 1,0:00:44.57,0:00:47.78,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}一小匙的閃耀
Dialogue: 1,0:00:47.78,0:00:50.91,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}便能化為一抹微笑
Dialogue: 1,0:00:50.91,0:00:57.70,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}或許那是悄悄埋下的願望
Dialogue: 1,0:00:58.00,0:01:00.71,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}讓奇蹟綻放
Dialogue: 1,0:01:00.96,0:01:07.67,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}將那最最重要的寶物找到
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.67,0:01:13.97,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}便是我們此行的目標
Dialogue: 1,0:01:13.97,0:01:20.69,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}雖不知能走多遠
Dialogue: 1,0:01:21.19,0:01:29.24,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\bord1}也要用希望編織當下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.48,0:00:07.99,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}どこまでいけるか分からないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:21.04,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}大丈夫　一人だっていいけど
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:28.22,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}本当はね　誰も一人じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.22,0:00:34.39,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}幸せが　寂しさが　不安も
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.81,0:00:43.94,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}全部味わうために生まれた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.57,0:00:47.78,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}一匙のきらめきで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.78,0:00:50.91,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}微笑みに変えていく
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.91,0:00:57.70,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}それは密かに願い込めた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.00,0:01:00.71,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}奇跡かも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:07.67,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}一番大事な宝物を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.67,0:01:13.97,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}見つけていくことが僕らの旅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.97,0:01:20.69,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}どこまでいけるか分からないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.19,0:01:29.24,ED-JP_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}目の前の今を希望で紡ぐよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.48,0:00:07.99,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}雖不知能走多遠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:21.04,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}沒關係  一個人也能過得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:28.22,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}但其實  沒有人是孤獨的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.22,0:00:34.39,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}幸福  寂寞  擔憂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.81,0:00:43.94,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}都是人生的必由之路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.57,0:00:47.78,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}一小匙的閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.78,0:00:50.91,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}便能化為一抹微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.91,0:00:57.70,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}或許那是悄悄埋下的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.00,0:01:00.71,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}讓奇蹟綻放
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.96,0:01:07.67,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}將那最最重要的寶物找到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.67,0:01:13.97,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}便是我們此行的目標
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.97,0:01:20.69,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}雖不知能走多遠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.19,0:01:29.24,ED-CH_EP01,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3\1a&HFF&}也要用希望編織當下
